{"id":170,"slug":"fishy-tales-with-the-seabream-sisters","url":"https://www.brightonfringe.org/events/fishy-tales-with-the-seabream-sisters/","title":"Fishy Tales With The Seabream Sisters","company":"Fran & Han Productions","genre":"Children & Young People","description":"Join the Seabream Sisters on the high seas for a rip-roaring storytelling adventure! Coral and Shelly might not catch many fish but they are experts at trawling the seas for stories, shanties and discarded treasure. Meet a salty sea worm with an astonishing secret, a grumpy lighthouse keeper who learns to love the sea, and find out how to calm a storm that’s shivering yer timbers. Don’t miss this voyage of discovery for the whole family, packed with original stories, clowning, puppetry and songs. You might even catch a fish! Nominated for the Family Friendly Award 2025 The Seabream Sisters completely captivated my children, who thoroughly adored the performance, and inspired them to play in a new way, again and again.","duration_minutes":45,"age_suitability":"3+","image_url":"https://content.brightonfringe.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/03-12-2025-225141-7140.jpg","website":"","instagram":"https://www.instagram.com/brightonfringe/","twitter":"https://twitter.com/brightonfringe","facebook":"https://www.facebook.com/brightonfringefestival","accessibility_features":["Assistance Dog"],"content_warnings":[],"cast":[],"scraped_at":"2026-05-19T15:09:33.695387","venue":{"id":50,"slug":"fishing-museum-loft-the-old-net-loft","name":"Fishing Museum Loft - The Old Net Loft","address":"200 King's Road Arches, East Sussex","url":"https://www.brightonfringe.org/venues/fishing-museum-loft-the-old-net-loft","lat":50.81998093537362,"lng":-0.14212891459465027},"performances":[{"id":31283,"date":"2026-05-31","time":"","standard_price":null,"concession_price":null,"is_sold_out":false,"booking_url":""},{"id":31284,"date":"2026-05-02","time":"11:00","standard_price":10.0,"concession_price":10.0,"is_sold_out":false,"book